+/**
+ * Report wizard submit pipeline (dialog-scoped provider): shapes {@link ReportRequest}, validates
+ * dialog state, gathers email recipients for the request DTO, and calls InitiateReportRequest.
+ *
+ * Do not put here: child panel Rx coordination ({@link ReportWizardDialogPanelService}), attachments
+ * grid state ({@link ReportWizardGridService}), or modal open/close ({@link ReportWizardDialogService}).
